 <title>The ReflectionParameter class</title>
 <titleabbrev>ReflectionParameter</titleabbrev>

 <partintro>

<!-- {{{ ReflectionParameter intro -->
  <section xml:id="reflectionparameter.intro">
   &reftitle.intro;
   <para>
    The <classname>ReflectionParameter</classname> class retrieves
    information about function's or method's parameters.
   </para>
   <para>
    To introspect function parameters, first create an instance
    of the <classname>ReflectionFunction</classname> or
    <classname>ReflectionMethod</classname> classes and then use their
    <methodname>ReflectionFunctionAbstract::getParameters</methodname> method
    to retrieve an array of parameters.
   </para>
  </section>
<!-- }}} -->

